metadata.description: This souvenir program of “Quezon Carnival and Exposition” contains photos of different Quezon Province public officials, invitation, activities, events, and projects. The purpose of Exposition is to raise funds of the erection of fitting monument in front of the capitol building in the middle of Perez Park.
